---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Slime. Joanna Fluder — Michalina Sablik">
  <div class="container page-content">
    <h1>Slime. Joanna Fluder</h1>
    <p class="exhibition-detail-venue">Zachęta National Gallery of Art, Warsaw | 2025</p>
    <div class="exhibition-detail-body">
      <p>The exhibition features 140 recent gouaches on paper or canvas, and premiere installations created especially for the space of Zachęta. Fluder's work focuses on women's everyday experiences, motherhood, neurodivergence, creative work, the social role of care, and the relationship with the surroundings, especially nature.</p>
      <p>Recurring snail and insect motifs serve as metaphors for inconspicuous existence.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="exhibition-detail-credits">
      <p><strong>Dates:</strong> 24th July – 19th October 2025</p>
      <p><strong>Curator:</strong> Michalina Sablik</p>
      <p><strong>Photographer:</strong> Jakub Celej</p>
    </div>
    <div class="exhibition-gallery" style="margin-top: 2.5rem; display: grid; gap: 1rem;">
